radar._queryString:
{[s] s: flip select PE_Ratio_TTM, Forward_PE: ForwardPE, PEG_Ratio, Price_Sales_TTM: PriceSales_TTM, Price_Book_MRQ: PriceBook_MRQ from .stocks.fundamentals where s = sym 

    }

chart._queryString:
{[s] flip select Market_Cap: MarketCap,Enterprise_Value: EnterpriseValue, Revenue_TTM,Gross_Profit_TTM :GrossProfit_TTM, EBITDA_TTM, Net_Income_TTM: NetIncome_TTM, Total_Cash :TotalCash, Total_Debt_MRQ: TotalDebt_MRQ, Operating_Cash_Flow_TTM :OperatingCashFlow_TTM, Levered_Cash_Flow_TTM :LeveredCashFlow_TTM  from .stocks.fundamentals where s = sym 

    }

pie._queryString:
{[s] flip select score: AnalystScore_1_sBUY_to_5_sSELL, total: 5  from .stocks.fundamentals where s = Symbol 

    }

EODChart._queryString: {[s] select  from SharePrice where Share = s}
